{"id":10314,"date":"2024-01-11T13:34:42","date_gmt":"2020-06-11T08:04:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=10314"},"modified":"2024-10-26T12:29:24","modified_gmt":"2024-10-26T06:59:24","slug":"closet-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/closet-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Get Over Boring Cupboards with these Amazing Closet Design Ideas for Your Home!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Closets are simply classy and now is the right time to get inspired with our simple bedroom closet design ideas<\/em>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Imagine having that sprawling closet like Carrie Bradshaw or Harvey Specter and waking up to a sleekly organised one every day? Didn\u2019t it just pep you up right away? That\u2019s why custom made closets are made just for you and you must get one for yourself in this lifetime to experience its class and ease of convenience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>From accessories, shoes to valuables, makeup, and clothes, you can store it all in a closet. As they are built-in, they make your home look more seamless and organised. Yet in a few homes, they are not absolutely used because of lack of neat organisation, sleek storage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To assist you in choosing just the perfect closet, we got a few closet design ideas for you. You may choose the one that beautifully lets you store all your things and makes the best use of space as well. Go through them!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple Closet Design For Small Rooms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Not too fancy yet beautifully functional, a simple closet design works out in any kind of room. You may choose wood, fiber or even glass to create a beautiful yet no-frills attached closet. With just a bit of plan and organisation, this design would also be as functional as any luxurious one.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115806\/simple-closet-design-for-small-rooms.jpg\" alt=\"Simple closet design ideas for small rooms or modest rooms\" class=\"wp-image-10321\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115806\/simple-closet-design-for-small-rooms.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115806\/simple-closet-design-for-small-rooms-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115806\/simple-closet-design-for-small-rooms-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115806\/simple-closet-design-for-small-rooms-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Go for a simple closet design for your studio apartment or modest rooms<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Closet Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A thing of beauty is a joy forever and this modern closet design sums it up well. With a mix of open spaces, drawers, and separators, this design takes care of all your knick-knacks and at the same time comes across as an attractive focus bagger in your bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115701\/modern-closet-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modern closet design with a mix of open spaces, drawers and separators\" class=\"wp-image-10320\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115701\/modern-closet-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115701\/modern-closet-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115701\/modern-closet-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115701\/modern-closet-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">With its rich feel and functional design, modern closet designs are popular<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Shoe Closet Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Don\u2019t like repeating shoes? This shoe closet design is just made for you then! Absolutely organised and eye-catchy, we feel that everyone must have a stunning shoe closet design made for themselves! Smartly place it in your dressing area and see how many compliments it gets you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115318\/closet-design-ideas-for-shoes.jpg\" alt=\"Closet design ideas for shoes with a chic shoe closet design\" class=\"wp-image-10316\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115318\/closet-design-ideas-for-shoes.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115318\/closet-design-ideas-for-shoes-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115318\/closet-design-ideas-for-shoes-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115318\/closet-design-ideas-for-shoes-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Put all your footwear in a place with a chic shoe closet design in your chamber<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dressing Room Closet Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To make smart utilisation of space, you might just consider using your walk-in dressing room as a closet as well. With an accent mirror and neatly placed and designed racks, drawers, this closet design outshines the usual closet designs any day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115420\/dressing-room-closet-design.jpg\" alt=\"Dressing room closet design to save space, it is a closet design idea\" class=\"wp-image-10317\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115420\/dressing-room-closet-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115420\/dressing-room-closet-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115420\/dressing-room-closet-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/11115420\/dressing-room-closet-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Make use of dressing room closet design if you want to save space and have a dressing along with a closet for yourself<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"941\" height=\"2014\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/26122536\/6-closet-designs-maximise-space.jpg\" alt=\"6 clever closet designs to maximise space: built-in, adjustable shelves, sliding doors, LED lighting, double rods, shoe racks\" class=\"wp-image-60105\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/26122536\/6-closet-designs-maximise-space.jpg 941w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/26122536\/6-closet-designs-maximise-space-140x300.jpg 140w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/26122536\/6-closet-designs-maximise-space-478x1024.jpg 478w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/